          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1666093888472-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, cut the <strong>paneer</strong> into small bite-sized cubes</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>cubed paneer</strong> and cook for 4-5 min or until starting to brown, then transfer to a plate and set aside until later, reserve the pan</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
