    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the paneer is cooking, peel and finely slice the <strong>brown onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Chop the <strong>tomato<span class=\"text-danger\">[es] </span></strong>roughly</p><p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>ginger</strong></p><p>Slice the <strong>green</strong> <strong>chilli<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong> finely</p>",
